          "_customHTML": "<section data-bs-version=\"5.1\" class=\"article03 strengthm5\" group=\"Article\" mbr-class=\"{\n    'mbr-fullscreen': fullScreen,\n    'mbr-parallax-background': bg.parallax}\">\n    <mbr-parameters>\n        <header>Size</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Full Width\" name=\"fullWidth\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Top\" name=\"paddingTop\" min=\"0\" max=\"12\" step=\"1\" value=\"3\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Bottom\" name=\"paddingBottom\" min=\"0\" max=\"12\" step=\"1\" value=\"3\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Reverse\" name=\"reverseContent\">\n        <header>Show/Hide</header>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Label\" name=\"showLabel\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Title\" name=\"showTitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Subtitle\" name=\"showSubtitle\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Text\" name=\"showText\" checked>\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Buttons\" name=\"showButtons\" checked>\n        <header>Background</header>\n        <fieldset type=\"background\" name=\"bg\" parallax>\n            <input type=\"image\" title=\"Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\">\n            <input type=\"color\" title=\"Color\" value=\"#0c7bbd\" selected>\n        </fieldset>\n        <header condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">Fallback Image</header>\n        <input type=\"image\" title=\"Fallback Image\" value=\"../_images/background1.jpg\" name=\"fallBackImage\" condition=\"bg.type === 'video'\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Gradient\" name=\"showGradient\" condition=\"bg.type == 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Gradient Color\" value=\"#FCFBFA\" name=\"gradient\" condition=\"showGradient && bg.type == 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"checkbox\" title=\"Overlay\" name=\"overlay\" condition=\"bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"color\" title=\"Overlay Color\" name=\"overlayColor\" value=\"#ffffff\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n        <input type=\"range\" inline title=\"Opacity\" name=\"overlayOpacity\" min=\"0\" max=\"1\" step=\"0.1\" value=\"0.5\" condition=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\">\n    </mbr-parameters>\n\n    <div class=\"mbr-fallback-image disabled\" mbr-if=\"bg.type == 'video'\"></div>\n    <div class=\"mbr-overlay\" mbr-if=\"overlay && bg.type !== 'color'\" opacity=\"{{overlayOpacity}}\" bg-color=\"{{overlayColor}}\"></div>\n\n    <div mbr-class=\"{'container': !fullWidth, 'container-fluid': fullWidth}\">\n        <div class=\"row justify-content-center\" mbr-class=\"{'flex-row-reverse' : reverseContent}\">\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-6 card\">\n                <div class=\"content-wrapper\">\n                    <p class=\"mbr-label mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-label\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showLabel\">\n                        <b>Give to the Program</b></p>\n                    <div class=\"title-wrapper\" mbr-if=\"showTitle || showSubtitle\">\n                        <h2 class=\"mbr-section-title mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-title\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-5\" mbr-if=\"showTitle\">\n                            <b>Care Close to Home</b>\n                        </h2>\n                        <h3 class=\"mbr-section-subtitle mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-section-subtitle\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-2\" mbr-if=\"showSubtitle\">\n                            <b>Your Gift Matters</b>\n                        </h3>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"text-wrapper\">\n                        <p class=\"mbr-text mbr-fonts-style\" data-app-selector=\".mbr-text, .text-wrapper, .mbr-section-btn\" mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" mbr-if=\"showText\">AIHA is applying for multiple grants and expects substantial support over the next year, but immediate community giving is essential to start services and demonstrate island commitment. <br><br><b>Every dollar helps—no contribution is too small.</b><br>- Launch services this fall by underwriting mobile clinic days.<br>- Show grant foundations strong local backing.<br>- Keep care close to home for every neighbor.<br>\n<br>Give securely via Zeffy (100% fee-free) to help us reach launch. Prefer to pledge by email? That works too.<br><b><br></b></p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div mbr-buttons mbr-theme-style=\"display-7\" class=\"mbr-section-btn\" mbr-if=\"showButtons\" data-toolbar=\"-mbrBtnMove\"><a class=\"btn btn-danger\" href=\"https://www.zeffy.com/en-US/donation-form/anderson-island-healthcare-advocates\" data-app-placeholder=\"Type Text\"><span class=\"mobi-mbri mobi-mbri-right mbr-iconfont mbr-iconfont-btn\"></span>\n                            \n                            Donate Now\n                        </a></div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"col-12 col-lg-6 card\">\n                <div class=\"iframe-wrapper\">\n                    <iframe title=\"Donation Form\" src=\"https://www.zeffy.com/en-US/donation-form/anderson-island-healthcare-advocates#donation-step-1\" style=\"border: none; width: 100%; height: 100%;\" allowpaymentrequest allowtransparency=\"true\">\n                    </iframe>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n</section>",
